{"published time": "2024-02-20T14-56-57-03-00", "images": ["https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.21.jpeg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-1024x460.jpeg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-17.41.48-1024x460.jpeg"], "content": "<div class=\"el-single-thumbnail\">\n <img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.21.jpeg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.21.jpeg 1600w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.21-300x135.jpeg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.21-1024x460.jpeg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.21-768x345.jpeg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.21-1536x690.jpeg 1536w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.21-60x27.jpeg 60w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"719\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.21.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.21.jpeg\" width=\"1600\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n <p>\n  Centenas de passageiros bloquearam a esta\u00e7\u00e3o de \u00f4nibus do Morro Alto, na cidade de Vespasiano, regi\u00e3o metropolitana de BH, no in\u00edcio da manh\u00e3 do dia 19 de fevereiro, contra as p\u00e9ssimas condi\u00e7\u00f5es do transporte na regi\u00e3o. Os manifestantes tamb\u00e9m interditaram parcialmente a rodovia MG10, na altura da \u201cCidade Administrativa\u201d, sede do governo estadual. O protesto foi convocado pela Frente Popular pelo Transporte P\u00fablico.\n </p>\n <p>\n  A situa\u00e7\u00e3o do transporte p\u00fablico de MG tem sido cada vez mais denunciada por trabalhadores pelas p\u00e9ssimas condi\u00e7\u00f5es. Ve\u00edculos lotados, parados no meio do trajeto por problemas mec\u00e2nicos, ar-condicionado estragados, goteiras, at\u00e9 o absurdo de rodas se desprenderem dos \u00f4nibus em movimento, batidas por falta de freio ou mesmo inc\u00eandios nos ve\u00edculos por falta de manuten\u00e7\u00e3o j\u00e1 se tornaram parte da revoltante rotina dos usu\u00e1rios da Esta\u00e7\u00e3o Morro Alto, particularmente nas linhas do MOVE como a 501C e 503H que fazem o trajeto at\u00e9 a regi\u00e3o central da capital e cujas passagens custam R$ 7,70. Meses atr\u00e1s, manifestantes\n  <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/mg-passageiros-fecham-estacao-de-onibus-e-denunciam-pessimas-condicoes-na-regiao-metropolitana-da-capital/\">\n   fecharam a esta\u00e7\u00e3o de \u00f4nibus Justin\u00f3polis\n  </a>\n  , tamb\u00e9m em Vespasiano, para denunciar as condi\u00e7\u00f5es do transporte.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24.jpeg\">\n    <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-169245\" data-id=\"169245\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-1024x460.jpeg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-1024x460.jpeg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-300x135.jpeg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-768x345.jpeg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-1536x690.jpeg 1536w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-60x27.jpeg 60w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24.jpeg 1600w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"460\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-1024x460.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-08.08.24-1024x460.jpeg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   </a>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Protestos contra precariza\u00e7\u00e3o do transporte t\u00eam sido mais frequentes em MG. Foto: Banco de Dados AND\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-17.41.48.jpeg\">\n    <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-169244\" data-id=\"169244\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-17.41.48-1024x460.jpeg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-17.41.48-1024x460.jpeg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-17.41.48-300x135.jpeg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-17.41.48-768x345.jpeg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-17.41.48-60x27.jpeg 60w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-17.41.48.jpeg 1280w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"460\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-17.41.48-1024x460.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/WhatsApp-Image-2024-02-19-at-17.41.48-1024x460.jpeg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   </a>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    P\u00e9ssimas condi\u00e7\u00f5es v\u00e3o desde de superlota\u00e7\u00e3o at\u00e9 falta de ar e problemas mec\u00e2nicos. Foto: Banco de Dados AND\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  Esse ano, a luta popular segue. No in\u00edcio do ano,\n  <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/mg-centenas-se-reunem-em-protesto-contra-aumento-da-tarifa-dos-onibus/\">\n   um protesto tomou a capital mineira contra o aumento da tarifa\n  </a>\n  , que subiu de R$ 4,50 para R$ 5,25 em Belo Horizonte e chega a atingir R$ 20 reais nos \u00f4nibus metropolitanos.\n </p>\n</div>\n", "source": "https://anovademocracia.com.br/mg-protesto-contra-sucateamento-do-transporte-publico/", "type": "article", "title": "MG: Protesto contra sucateamento do transporte p\u00fablico - A Nova Democracia", "description": "Centenas de passageiros bloquearam a esta\u00e7\u00e3o de \u00f4nibus Morro Alto, em Vespasiano, contra as p\u00e9ssimas condi\u00e7\u00f5es do transporte p\u00fablico.", "modified time": "2024-02-20T14:56:59-03:00", "updated time": "2024-02-20T14:56:59-03:00", "author": ["Comit\u00ea de Apoio \u2013 Belo Horizonte (MG)"], "categories": ["Nacional"], "tags": ["Luta Classista"], "sections": ["Nacional"], "link-section": "nacional"}